OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'He was like a lighthouse' 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F- Sidney Poitier's daughter
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fposts moving tribute       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sidney Poitier's daughter has posted a 
OL,6, lengthy and emotional tribute to her   
OL,7, father after the Hollywood veteran's   
OL,8, death last week at the age of 94.      
OL,10,FThe trailblazing actor, humanitarian   
OL,11,Fand diplomat was the first black man to
OL,12,Fwin best actor at the Oscars.          
OL,14,FIn an 800-word tribute posted on       
OL,15,FInstagram, Sydney Poitier praised her  
OL,16,Ffather's "strength of character and    
OL,17,Fmoral fortitude".                      
OL,19,F"But what I really want people to know 
OL,20,Fis how GOOD he was," she wrote.        
OL,23,D]G     From the BBC News Website       
